OL,3,CMarket stallholder cousins convicted
OL,4,Cof grooming five teenage girls for sex
OL,6,FTwo market stallholders have been
OL,7,Fconvicted of sexually abusing five
OL,8,Fvulnerable teenage girls after
OL,9,Fgrooming them in the late 1990s.
OL,11,FCousins Manzorr Hussain, 54, and
OL,12,FImtiaz Ali, 53, initially came into
OL,13,Fcontact with some of their victims at
OL,14,Ftheir workplace and later plied them
OL,15,Fwith alcohol and drugs before multiple
OL,16,Foffences, including rape, were
OL,17,Fcommitted.
