OL,3,CMarket stallholder cousins convicted
OL,4,Cof grooming five teenage girls for sex
OL,6,FThe abuse mainly took place in Bury,
OL,7,FGreater Manchester, but also elsewhere
OL,8,Fin the region and parts of Wales
OL,9,Fincluding at private homes, vehicles,
OL,10,Fa hotel and a car dealership, said the
OL,11,FCrown Prosecution Service (CPS).
OL,13,FAli staged "sex parties" where
OL,14,Fmultiple men targeted the girls, while
OL,15,FHussain arranged for one girl to
OL,16,Fperform sex acts with strangers on a
OL,17,Fdirty mattress in a flat.
