OL,3,CMarket stallholder cousins convicted
OL,4,Cof grooming five teenage girls for sex
OL,6,FOne victim said she was threatened
OL,7,Fthat if she did not comply she would
OL,8,Fbe abandoned naked on the moors, said
OL,9,Fthe CPS.
OL,11,FThe offences took place on various
OL,12,Fdates between 1996 and 1999 when the
OL,13,Fvictims were aged 13 to 16.
OL,15,FOn Monday, 27 October, Hussain, of
OL,16,FManchester Road, Bury, was convicted
OL,17,Fby a jury at Manchester Minshull
OL,18,FStreet Crown of seven offences of rape.
