OL,6,FAli, of Ainsworth Road, Radcliffe, was
OL,7,Ffound guilty of five counts of rape,
OL,8,Ffive counts of indecent assault and
OL,9,Fone count of indecent assault.
OL,11,FCPS specialist prosecutor Claire
OL,12,FBrinton said: "They showed a callous
OL,13,Fdisregard for the girls' welfare and
OL,14,Fused manipulation, force, threats and
OL,15,Ffear to control them and make them
OL,16,Fcomply with their sick demands.
