OL,6,F"These women have demonstrated
OL,7,Fremarkable bravery in coming forward,
OL,8,Fremaining engaged with the legal
OL,9,Fprocess, and reliving deeply traumatic
OL,10,Fexperiences from over two decades ago.
OL,11,FI would like to thank all of them and
OL,12,FI hope these convictions can bring
OL,13,Fthem some comfort."
OL,15,FSergeant Daniel Whittaker, of Greater
OL,16,FManchester Police, said: "This case
OL,17,Frepresents a harrowing example of
OL,18,Fpredatory behaviour by two men who
OL,19,Fdeliberately targeted vulnerable
OL,20,Fchildren.
