OL,6,F"The offenders were plying the victims
OL,7,Fwith alcohol and drugs and taking them
OL,8,Fto numerous locations before sexually
OL,9,Fabusing and assaulting them.
OL,11,F"They exploited their positions of
OL,12,Ftrust and manipulated the girls into
OL,13,Fbelieving they were in relationships,
OL,14,Fwhile in reality they were being used
OL,15,Ffor sexual gratification."
OL,17,FHussain and Ali will be sentenced on 8
OL,18,FDecember.
